    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "What He is of God and of Man as the Son,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We now may enjoy since with Him we are one;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our High Priest and Captain—salvation is He!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’ll cause us to grow in His glory to be."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s washed all our sins, purified them fore’er;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Tasted death on the cross, ended slavery there."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He took on our nature, the devil has slain,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And put you and me in His glorious train."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So great the extent of salvation to us—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’re partners of Christ in His plan glorious."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’ll bring us to glory and we’ll rule with Him,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To the uttermost saved by His working within."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To such a salvation our heed we must give,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lest drifting away or neglecting we live."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Christ now as our life, future ruling with Him,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’ll miss if we miss this salvation within."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "“So great a salvation” is given to us"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That we may be made like our Lord glorious!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "By all that He is and by all He has done"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’re brought into glory with God’s firstborn Son."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "6"
    }
